# 🚲 Bike Sharing End-to-End Analysis

> An end-to-end data analytics project covering exploratory data analysis, predictive forecasting, and interactive business intelligence — built for a professional portfolio.

---

## 📌 Project Overview

This project analyzes two years of bike-sharing rental data (2011–2012) from a Washington D.C. bike-share system, examining behavioral patterns, weather sensitivity, hourly demand cycles, and seasonal trends across two distinct user types: **Casual** and **Registered** riders.

The analysis culminates in a fully interactive **Power BI dashboard** with five report pages, supported by a Python-based EDA and a Prophet time-series forecast.

