## 🧠 Key Findings

| Finding | Detail |
|---|---|
| Registered riders dominate | 81.17% of total rentals (2.67M vs 620K casual) |
| Peak hour | 5 PM — 75× higher than the 4 AM low |
| Fastest growing hour | 5 AM — 76.5% YoY increase |
| Highest rental month | August — 351,194 rentals (10.67% of annual) |
| Weather sensitivity | Non-clear conditions reduce rentals ~22% on average |
| Humidity effect | 63% decline from optimal (21–40%) to maximum humidity |
| Forecast growth | 29.71% projected increase — 2M → 2.66M rentals |

