## 💡 Business Recommendations

1. **Early-bird incentive (5–10% discount)** targeting the 5–7 AM window to accelerate the fastest-growing commuter segment
2. **Sunny-day promotional packages** to capitalize on clear-weather demand spikes — nearly 5× higher than adverse conditions
3. **Winter maintenance windows** (December–February) for fleet servicing — lowest demand period with only 14.32% of annual rentals
4. **Registered rider retention focus** — as the core customer base driving 81% of revenue, loyalty programs offer the highest ROI

